    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The SPA is designed as an executive dashboard with three core, non-linear sections: "The Vision" (Business Plan), "The Opportunity" (Market Analysis), and "The Execution" (GTM Strategy). This thematic structure, navigated by a sticky header, allows stakeholders (investors, team members) to explore the plan based on their specific interests, rather than being forced into a linear document flow. For example, a marketing lead can jump directly to "The Execution," while a financial analyst can focus on the interactive charts in "The Vision." This user-centric design prioritizes exploration and synthesis over passive reading, making the complex strategy more digestible and engaging. Key interactions include dynamic chart filtering, clickable competitor cards, and an interactive GTM timeline, all designed to reveal deeper layers of information on demand. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Financial Projections: Report Info -> 3-Year Forecast. Goal -> Show growth & path to profitability. Viz -> Interactive Line Chart (Chart.js). Interaction -> Toggle visibility of Revenue, Expenses, EBITDA. Justification -> More dynamic and comparative than a static table.
        - Market Sizing (TAM/SAM/SOM): Report Info -> Market sizing data. Goal -> Visualize market scale and focus. Viz -> Interactive Donut Chart (Chart.js). Interaction -> Hover for details. Justification -> Intuitively shows the "slice of the pie" strategy.
        - Competitive Analysis: Report Info -> Competitor strengths/weaknesses. Goal -> Compare directly. Viz -> HTML/CSS Grid with clickable cards. Interaction -> Click to expand/collapse details. Justification -> Encourages active comparison and is more engaging than a static matrix.
        - SWOT Analysis: Report Info -> SWOT points. Goal -> Organize strategic factors. Viz -> 2x2 HTML/CSS Grid. Interaction -> Click to reveal details in a modal/expanded view. Justification -> Clean, organized, and interactive presentation of core strategic pillars.
        - GTM Rollout: Report Info -> Phased GTM plan. Goal -> Show timeline and activities. Viz -> Horizontal HTML/CSS Timeline. Interaction -> Click phase to see details. Justification -> Clearly visualizes the project's temporal roadmap.
        - KPIs: Report Info -> KPI targets. Goal -> Demonstrate measurable success metrics. Viz -> Bar Chart (Chart.js). Interaction -> Dropdown to select and view different KPIs. Justification -> Allows focused analysis of specific success metrics over time.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
